ew with the sunday times archived january   at the wayback machine  goldman offers m apology for crisis financial times november    goldman sachs blankfein says libor scandal undermines trust bloomberg businessweek july   retrieved february     goldman ceo blankfein said to meet with obama adviser lew bloomberg businessweek july   retrieved february     emeritus board robin hood foundation retrieved october     board of directors partnership for new york city retrieved october     board of overseers weill cornell medical college retrieved october     rivard december   all in the family inside higher ed retrieved october     julia la roche hey look lloyd blankfeins kids are on instagram business insider july    harvard alumni  de la merced michael j september   lloyd blankfein goldman sachs ceo has lymphoma the new york times retrieved october     belvedere matthew j february   goldmans blankfein us economy not off rails cnbc retrieved october   bald and without his beard the yearold blankfein also talked about battling cancer he said hes feeling pretty good after undergoing like  hours of chemo over the last few months   how goldman sachs’ ceo beat cancer fortune october   retrieved october    external linksedit profile at goldman sachs profile at bloomberg businessweek appearances on cspan lloyd blankfein on charlie rose lloyd blankfein collected news and commentary the guardian  lloyd blankfein collected news and commentary at international business times lloyd blankfein collected news and commentary the new york times  lloyd blankfein collected news and commentary the wall street journal  goldman runs risks reaps rewards the new york times june   the man goldman is banking on  profile from businessweek magazine business positions preceded by henry paulson chairman and ceo goldman sachs –present succeeded by incumbent v t e goldman sachs notable current executives lloyd c blankfein ceo harvey schwartz notable former executives mark carney gary cohn henry paulson r